1
00:00:12,560 --> 00:00:14,000
Wang Ning.

2
00:00:25,760 --> 00:00:27,280
Adjust your pose a little.

3
00:00:27,440 --> 00:00:29,400
Lift your head and look up slightly.

4
00:00:29,400 --> 00:00:30,920
Okay. 3, 2, 1.

5
00:00:31,280 --> 00:00:33,000
One more shot.

6
00:00:33,160 --> 00:00:35,600
3, 2, 1. Okay.

7
00:00:42,480 --> 00:00:44,800
Does the brand want Yin Zixi as the model?

8
00:00:45,680 --> 00:00:47,520
I've received the proposal.

9
00:00:48,040 --> 00:00:50,160
Yeah, okay. That's all.

10
00:00:52,720 --> 00:00:54,760
I see you're busy every day.

11
00:00:55,160 --> 00:00:56,920
How much of the target have you completed?

12
00:00:56,920 --> 00:00:57,980
It's already done.

13
00:00:58,200 --> 00:00:59,280
Impossible.

14
00:00:59,360 --> 00:01:01,290
The company didn't even notify me.

15
00:01:02,480 --> 00:01:04,319
Did you plant a spy?

16
00:01:04,319 --> 00:01:05,280
Ah.

17
00:01:05,600 --> 00:01:07,760
Don't just think about work all day.

18
00:01:07,840 --> 00:01:08,880
I heard

19
00:01:08,880 --> 00:01:10,440
Yin Zixi is very popular

20
00:01:10,520 --> 00:01:11,960
over at the school.

21
00:01:13,160 --> 00:01:16,220
Uncle He, are you worried we'll catch up with the quota?

22
00:01:16,560 --> 00:01:18,960
I'm worried you'll act like a block of wood.

23
00:01:19,240 --> 00:01:21,039
Don't regret it when Yin Zixi is pursued

24
00:01:21,039 --> 00:01:22,600
by someone else.

25
00:01:25,800 --> 00:01:28,360
Okay, let's continue.

26
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:31,000
Move back a bit first.

27
00:01:31,520 --> 00:01:33,080
Move back a little more.

28
00:01:33,080 --> 00:01:33,759
Ah.

29
00:01:36,600 --> 00:01:37,330
Are you okay?

30
00:01:37,640 --> 00:01:38,360
I'm fine.

31
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:44,520
That's it for today's shooting.

32
00:01:44,520 --> 00:01:45,650
Good job, everyone.

33
00:01:53,240 --> 00:01:54,759
I just sprained my ankle.

34
00:01:54,759 --> 00:01:56,490
I'll be fine after a short rest.

35
00:01:56,920 --> 00:01:58,920
I can shoot as long as I stand still.

36
00:01:59,920 --> 00:02:01,450
We are taking a break today.

37
00:02:04,080 --> 00:02:05,200
I'll do it myself.

38
00:02:07,240 --> 00:02:08,759
Sit still.

39
00:02:13,080 --> 00:02:14,160
What's wrong?

40
00:02:23,320 --> 00:02:24,480
Hello, Uncle He.

41
00:02:24,840 --> 00:02:26,320
Your father just called.

42
00:02:26,480 --> 00:02:27,520
The investigation is over.

43
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:28,520
He just came back.

44
00:02:29,880 --> 00:02:30,520
Really?

45
00:02:30,600 --> 00:02:31,660
It's quite urgent.

46
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:33,060
I need to go back first.

47
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:34,050
Got it, Uncle He.

48
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:35,440
Can I go back then?

49
00:02:35,720 --> 00:02:37,040
The flight is at 11:00 tonight.

50
00:02:37,040 --> 00:02:38,440
Come if you can make it.

51
00:02:38,760 --> 00:02:39,680
Okay.

52
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:42,680
My dad is back.

53
00:02:43,280 --> 00:02:44,680
That's great.

54
00:02:57,240 --> 00:02:59,570
You've been living off-campus all along?

55
00:02:59,600 --> 00:03:01,240
There's an apartment above the restaurant.

56
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:02,040
It's more convenient to live here.

57
00:03:02,040 --> 00:03:03,970
It's more convenient to live here.

58
00:03:04,120 --> 00:03:07,320
No wonder you don't interact much with other classmates.

59
00:03:17,560 --> 00:03:18,800
Let's go.

60
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:29,280
President, she's here.

61
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:31,680
You must be Wen.

62
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:34,400
What do you want?

63
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:37,560
Haven't I already written the self-criticism for cheating?

64
00:03:37,560 --> 00:03:39,560
Ah, you misunderstood.

65
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:40,960
I asked you to come here

66
00:03:40,960 --> 00:03:42,520
mainly because I want to cooperate with you.

67
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:43,520
Cooperate?

68
00:03:44,200 --> 00:03:46,320
I don't want to join your student union.

69
00:03:46,320 --> 00:03:48,920
I heard you don't get along well with Yin Zixi.

70
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:55,200
Let's cooperate.

71
00:04:01,040 --> 00:04:03,160
I'll be back in a few days.

72
00:04:05,600 --> 00:04:06,520
Okay.

73
00:04:07,680 --> 00:04:09,120
Can you handle it alone?

74
00:04:10,040 --> 00:04:10,840
I can.

75
00:04:11,320 --> 00:04:14,180
I know all the equipment in the live broadcast room.

76
00:04:18,959 --> 00:04:20,000
Hey.

77
00:04:20,200 --> 00:04:21,959
Is your foot still injured?

78
00:04:22,640 --> 00:04:23,800
I told you it's fine.

79
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:25,130
I'm already recovered.

80
00:04:25,520 --> 00:04:26,880
Look.

81
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:36,480
Zixi,

82
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:38,800
I have something to tell you.

83
00:04:38,800 --> 00:04:39,920
The car is here.

84
00:04:41,320 --> 00:04:50,520
Xi A 6M223.

85
00:05:02,200 --> 00:05:03,760
Wait for me.

86
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:05,520
Okay.

87
00:05:59,520 --> 00:06:00,850
That's a wrap for today.

88
00:06:00,880 --> 00:06:02,200
Great job, everyone.

89
00:06:22,360 --> 00:06:23,020
Yue S Z545U.

90
00:06:25,320 --> 00:06:27,000
Look, that's the woman.

91
00:06:27,280 --> 00:06:28,560
Let's go.

92
00:06:45,440 --> 00:06:47,200
Hurry up.

93
00:06:54,960 --> 00:06:55,600
Go.

94
00:06:57,200 --> 00:06:58,840
An, bad news.

95
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:01,080
Someone's trying to harm Yin Zixi.

96
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:11,600
Driver, turn around.

97
00:07:11,640 --> 00:07:12,480
What's wrong?

98
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:14,140
Turn around. I need to go back.

99
00:07:38,840 --> 00:07:39,680
Ah.

100
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:41,600
What do you want?

101
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:42,929
I've called the police.

102
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:44,400
Oh, really?

103
00:08:44,800 --> 00:08:45,800
Don't be nervous.

104
00:08:46,160 --> 00:08:47,280
We are not bad guys.

105
00:08:47,640 --> 00:08:51,040
Internet celebrities like you are just selling yourselves.

106
00:08:51,240 --> 00:08:52,170
Name your price.

107
00:08:53,400 --> 00:08:54,660
Money is not a problem.

108
00:08:55,680 --> 00:08:56,940
Don't come any closer.

109
00:08:57,400 --> 00:08:58,920
If you come any closer, I'll scream.

110
00:08:58,920 --> 00:08:59,880
Scream.

111
00:09:00,560 --> 00:09:02,840
No one will hear you even if you scream your lungs out.

112
00:09:02,840 --> 00:09:04,900
Why don't you play with us for a while?

113
00:09:04,920 --> 00:09:06,560
We'll treat you well.

114
00:09:16,920 --> 00:09:17,840
Just you wait.

115
00:09:22,880 --> 00:09:23,720
How are you?

116
00:09:23,840 --> 00:09:24,960
Are you okay?

117
00:09:29,920 --> 00:09:31,360
Why are you here?

118
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:34,360
It's the completely wrong direction from the school.

119
00:09:34,480 --> 00:09:36,340
Because I'm bad with directions.

120
00:09:41,360 --> 00:09:43,720
So what?

121
00:09:45,840 --> 00:09:46,840
Okay.

122
00:09:58,800 --> 00:10:00,760
Liu Mingde

